<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> die von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                        als <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns von <expan>Ros<ex>enberg</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>schulth<ex>eisz</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hett von des entsagens
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns
                            <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Seman und <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> getan
                                <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>, also hat uns der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hans von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> einen
                        brief gezögt, den ir im <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> geschikt und
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, daz ir
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> veyntschaft <add>mit</add> den
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>erman</ex></expan> Seman und <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>abgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt. Und also wissen wir mit den <pb facs="#facs_42" id="21r"/><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>erman</ex></expan>
<expan>Sema<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Ros<ex>emberg</ex></expan> niht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> denn <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
                        und guts ze schiken ze <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in fürbas
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> keins argen
                            <expan>gewart<ex>en</ex></expan>, on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                        Denn wir <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir ewch in den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gemüet und so
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweiset habt. Und wa wir ewch
                        lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan>, des <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir auch
                        willig sein und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
